snippet.title: Mystical Sovereign Z Trailer
snippet.description:
Trailer for Mystical Sovereign Z.

Steam page:
https://store.steampowered.com/app/3196980/Mystical_Sovereign_Z/

Mystical Sovereign Z is a sci-fi/fantasy hybrid strategy game. Experience real time battles and turn based strategy with various RPG elements and choices to be made along the way.

Trailer music: cynicmusic - Hyperflight Racing, Vitalezzz - Apparatus Overlord
